Next Steps:
1. Get the route URL (OpenShift):
   oc get route drupal-ingress -n msu

2. Forward port to access (optional):
   oc port-forward svc/drupal 8443:443 -n msu

3. Open browser: https://drupal.local (or https://localhost:8443)

4. Run Drupal web installer and configure:
   - Database: PostgreSQL
   - Host: drupal-postgres-primary.msu.svc.cluster.local
   - Database: drupal_db
   - User: drupal_user
   - Password: (see above)

Note: Self-signed certificate will show security warning - this is expected.

